{"about_the_game":"Battle for your companion's survival as you explore a mysterious, vibrant, and crumbling world full of dangers and secrets to discover.  Evie is an action-adventure game with an HD-2D visual style that plays out like a modernized version of SNES and Genesis classics.<br><br>UNBREAKABLE BOND<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2470910/extras/ForestWalkGood_SMALL_SHORT.gif?t=1736831202\" /><br>With Evie's help, her friend battles their way back from serious illness as the two bond throughout an epic adventure.<br><br>FIND YOUR OWN PATH<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2470910/extras/BombGood_SMALL.gif?t=1736831202\" /><br>Exploration is rewarded and certain magical abilities will make specific encounters easier, while other abilities may be the key to unlocking a secret area.<br><br>FACE YOUR FEAR<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2470910/extras/CombatGood_SMALL.gif?t=1736831202\" /><br>A fluid combat system allows players to use magic, dash behind enemies, drop traps, block, parry, and deflect projectiles.  Play your way and focus on skills and abilities that match your play style.<br><br>HD-2D visuals merge hand drawn sprites into a 3D world in a real time action-adventure game.<br>Lots of secret areas to discover, making way for helpful items on your journey.<br>Uncover a diverse set of new magical abilities.<br>Overcome a formidable boss at each distinctive biome to earn new abilities.","background":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/2470910?t=1736831202","background_raw":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/2470910?t=1736831202","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2470910/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1736831202","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.